title: Dallas 10x02 Return to Camelot part2.avi
description:
The long dream is over.
Yes boys and girls, autobots and decepticons, illegal aliens and crossdressers all-alike: DALLAS is back with season 10!


J.R hopes to get Donna away from Dallas; Jenna has problems with Charlie; a disaster strikes Ewing 12; Sue Ellen tracks J.R. and Mandy; a new ranch hand is hired at Southfork.

First Aired: 9/26/1986

Though last season was supposed to be a dream, at least one portion was almost psychic in nature: ranch hand Ben Stivers (now named Wes Parmalee) carried over from last season to this season.
